      • Question

        public Question(java.lang.String question,
                java.lang.String answer,
                java.lang.String correctText)
        Constructor takes name of the picture, name of the author and the text after the correct answer. The number of correct answer will be generated automatically. The other 3 authors also will be generated randomly.
        Parameters:
        question - Name of the picture for the question
        answer - Correct name of the artist
        correctText - The text that will be shown after the right answer
